-kelly-named-to-team-usa-collegiate-national-team</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/5/baseball-kelly-named-to-team-usa-collegiate-national-team</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Gavin Kelly takes a swing against UNC with the Team USA Collegiate National Team Logo featured" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/7/5/WVU_BSB_G4_CWS_v_UNC_0917_largeTeam_USA.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – West Virginia University's Gavin Kelly has been named to the 28-man Collegiate National Team that will represent Team USA and compete in the inaugural World Collegiate Baseball Championship at Taichung City Intercontinental Baseball Stadium in Taichung City, Taiwan, from July 11-15.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/5/WVU_BSB_G4_CWS_v_UNC_0917_largeTeam_USA.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/5/WVU_BSB_G4_CWS_v_UNC_0917_largeTeam_USA.jpg"><media:title>Gavin Kelly takes a swing against UNC with the Team USA Collegiate National Team Logo featured</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/5/WVU_BSB_G4_CWS_v_UNC_0917_largeTeam_USA.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 5 Jul 2026 13:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59226</s:story_id></item><item><title>New Flagship Affiliates for MSN Radio from Learfield</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/1/athletics-communications-new-flagship-affiliates-for-msn-radio-from-learfield</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/7/1/athletics-communications-new-flagship-affiliates-for-msn-radio-from-learfield</guid><category>General, Athletics 