nt coach.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/1/WRESTLE_WELCOMECOACH_HALL_1920x1080_Ali.png" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/1/WRESTLE_WELCOMECOACH_HALL_1920x1080_Ali.png"><media:title>Peyton Hall was hired as an assistant coach for the wrestling program in July 2026.</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/7/1/WRESTLE_WELCOMECOACH_HALL_1920x1080_Ali.png" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 1 Jul 2026 08:59:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>18</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59223</s:story_id></item><item><title>Eighty-One Mountaineers Named to 2026 Spring Academic All-Big 12 Team</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/30/general-eighty-one-mountaineers-named-to-2026-spring-academic-all-big-12-team</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/6/30/general-eighty-one-mountaineers-named-to-2026-spring-academic-all-big-12-team</guid><category>General</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Graphic for the Spring Academic All-Big 12 Team" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/6/30/Athletics26_SpringAcademicAllBig12_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – A total of 81 student-athletes from West Virginia University have been named to the 2026 Spring Academic All-Big 12 Conference Team as announced by the Big 12.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/6/30/Athletics26_SpringAcademicAllBig12_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images